text: Borei O'Svay Sen Chey District () is a newly established district located in Stung Treng Province, Cambodia according to Sub Decree No. 06.http://freshnewsasia.com/index.php/en/localnews/111799-2019-01-29-11-34-21.html Borei O'Svay Sen Chey District is divided into three communes – O'Svay, Koh Sneng, and Preah Romkel – which were previously part of Thala Borivat District.https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/government-establishes-new- districts-town-better-management ==Administration== The following table shows the villages of Borei O'Svay Sen Chey District by communes. {| class="wikitable" !
